Package org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords

Class Coordinate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Coordinate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinnedCoordinate, EquatorialPoint, GeocentricPoint, PhysicalCoordinate, Point, PolCoordinate, SphericalPoint, TimeStamp
    @Embeddable
@MappedSuperclass
@VoDml(id="coords:Coordinate",
       role=dataType)
public abstract class Coordinate
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
    Abstract base class for the Coordinate data types which represent an absolute location within a coordinate space. Coordinates MUST refer to a coordinate system, providing additional metadata relevant to interpreting the coordinate value, and its representation. dataType: Coordinate
